#, fuzzy
msgid "A Tale of Two Brothers - Epilogue"
msgstr "Historia Duorum Fratrum"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/5_Epilog.cfg:11
msgid ""
"After a long battle with many losses the orc was finally slain. It took "
"several years to rebuild the village and the surrounding barnyards. For the "
"moment the people were safe again and knew that help was close should such a "
"danger ever reoccur."
msgstr ""

